INSERT INTO `keyboards` VALUES ('10066887','Microsoft Natural Ergonomic Keyboard','59.99','Breakthrough Ergonomic Keyboard Design with improved design promotes a more natural hand, wrist, and forearm position for greater comfort. Perform common tasks, like opening documents and replying to e-mail, with the touch of a button.','<ul><li>Advanced, ergonomic split keyboard design.</li><li>Enhanced curved key layout for easier reach.</li><li>Reverse slope for a more natural wrist posture.</li><li>Enhanced sloped shape and curved key layout promotes natural hand position for greater comfort.</li><li>Padded palm rest with removable palm lift encourages a more natural and comfortable wrist posture.</li><li>Intuitive Zoom Slider lets you zoom in quickly and accurately for a closer look.</li><li>System Requirements: Win2000/XP Home Or Professional Edition, Pentium 233MHz Or Higher Processor And 128MB RAM, 100MB Hard Disk Space, CD Drive, USB Port.</li></ul>'),('10201435','Logitech Wireless Keyboard (K360) - Black','29.99','This compact wireless keyboard lets you type in more comfort with a layout you\'re used to. It prevents you from hunching over your laptop to type. And it\'s about 20% smaller than our standard keyboards, so it fits in your office, your living room or wherever you use your computer.','<ul><li>Setup is a breeze, too. You just plug the receiver in, pull the battery tab and start IMing smiley faces to your friends and frenemies.</li><li>Want to turn up the volume on a YouTube clip? Or jump right to your Facebook page? It\'s all at your fingertips with six hot keys and 12 programmable F-keys for instant access to the Internet, e-mail, play/pause, volume and more.</li><li>Logitech Advanced 2.4 GHz wireless connectivity gives you the reliability of a cord plus wireless convenience and freedom-fast data transmission, virtually no delays or dropouts, and 128-bit AES encryption.</li><li>The tiny Logitech Unifying receiver is small enough to stay in your laptop, so there\'s no need to unplug it when you move around. Plus, you can easily add another compatible mouse, keyboard or number pad-without the hassle of multiple USB receivers.</li><li>Compact Comfort: The perfect laptop companion - this compact keyboard lets you type with more comfort while taking up less space.</li><li>Power-Packed: The three-year battery life is so hassle-free you just might forget it uses batteries at all.</li><li>Just One Touch: You can do more, faster with six hot keys and twelve programmable F-keys for instant access to music, e-mail and more.</li></ul>'),('10204751','Logitech Solar Wireless Keyboard for Mac (K750)','89.99','Free yourself from the hassle of wires and batteries with the light-powered Logitech Wireless Solar Keyboard K750 for Mac. It charges up whenever there\'s light and it stays charged for at least three months, even in total darkness. It has all the familiar Mac keys, including a Mission Control hot key, and it works right out of the box.','<ul><li>Powered by light - even indoors - making battery concerns a thing of the past</li><li>It works wherever you do: your home, office, hotel room, etc.</li><li>Charges with lamp light or sunlight, indoors or outdoors</li><li>On a full charge it can work up to three months, even in total darkness</li><li>Free Solar App provides a handy lux meter that tells you how much power you have left</li><li>Only 1/3\" thick with sleek, stylish lines and a thin profile</li><li>Includes all the usual Mac keys, such as music and brightness controls, command, and eject</li><li>The Logitech-only concave key cap design provides faster, quieter typing with a better feel</li><li>Wireless technology gives you the freedom to work or play wherever you like, and the 2.4GHz frequency virtually eliminates delays, dropouts, and interference</li><li>Created using eco-friendly practices, like PVC-free construction and fully recyclable box</li><li>Setup takes only seconds - just plug the wireless receiver into a USB on your computer and start using the computer right away, no software installation required</li><li>The tiny Logitech unifying receiver is small enough to stay in your laptop all the time, and you can add other compatible wireless products - like a mouse or additional keyboard - without having to plug in multiple USB receivers</li></ul>'),('10397223','Razer BlackWidow Ultimate 2016 Mechanical','89.99','Get ready for gaming guts and glory with the Razer BlackWidow Ultimate mechanical gaming keyboard. Boost your gaming with speedy and responsive performance and programmable backlit keys that give you the tactical edge.','<ul><li>Full mechanical keys actuate at an optimal distance so your deft fingers can fly across the keyboard no matter how intense your gaming marathons get</li><li>Designed to withstand up to 80 million keystrokes</li><li>Mechanical Switch technology delivers optimum keyboard speed and responsiveness </li><li>Never miss a key in the dark with programmable backlit keys that give you the tactical edge, letting you launch assaults and flank your foes even under low-light conditions </li><li>Jazz up your gaming station with dynamic lighting effects </li></ul>'),('10397381','Apple Magic Keyboard (MLA22LL/A)','129.99','A sleek design, built-in rechargeable battery, and enhanced key features team up to bring you the convenient and comfortable Apple Magic Keyboard. Its improved scissor mechanism beneath each key offers increased stability, while optimized key travel and a lower profile provide a very comfortable and precise typing experience.','<ul><li>This wireless keyboard pairs automatically with your Mac via Bluetooth so you can get to work straight away</li><li>Features a built-in rechargeable battery so youâ€™ll eliminate the use of traditional batteries</li><li>Battery will power your device for about a month or more before needing a recharge</li><li>Enhanced scissor mechanism beneath keys provide added stability</li><li>Optimized key travel and lower profile deliver a super comfortable and precise typing experience</li><li>Language: English</li></ul>'),('10403255','Logitech K380 Multi-Device Bluetooth Keyboard - Grey','29.99','The endless fumbling and fixing that comes with a touchscreen keyboard can be a hair-pulling experience. This Logitech K380 Multi-Device Bluetooth keyboard easily syncs up with your device and lets you enjoy a natural desktop keyboard-based typing experience. It\'s highly mobile and can be taken on the go with you.','<ul><li>Easily connect to and type on all your computing devices, including smartphones, tablets, and more</li><li>Compatible with Windows, Mac, Chrome OS, Android, iOS (iPhone and iPad), and Apple TV </li><li>Compact keyboard you can take anywhere in the home or carry it with you on the go!</li><li>Connect with up to three devices simultaneously using the Easy-Switch button </li><li>Recognizes each device and automatically maps keys to give you a familiar layout with your favourite shortcuts </li><li>Two years of battery life from two pre-installed AAA batteries, virtually eliminates battery worries </li></ul>'),('12428898','Razer Cynosa Chroma Backlit Gaming Keyboard','79.99','The right keyboard can make all the difference in your gaming experience. The Razer Cynosa Chroma backlit gaming keyboard not only gives you superior gaming functionality to give you an edge on your competitors, it also gives you customizable backlighting and underglow lighting for a unique, personalized experience.','<ul><li>Keys are individually backlit so you can see clearly even in a dark room</li><li>Gaming grade keys are softly cushioned for a comfortable experience</li><li>Razer Chroma backlighting gives you 16.8 million color customization options</li><li>Underglow lighting gives you 22 customization zones</li><li>Fully programmable keys give you on-the-fly macro recording capabilities</li><li>Spill resistant construction is durable</li><li>Gaming mode option gives you an edge on your competitors</li><li>Razer Synapse enabled</li><li>10 key roll-over with anti-ghosting</li><li>Features gaming mode option and 1000Hz Ultrapolling</li></ul>'),('12513721','Corsair K68 Backlit Mechanical Cherry MX Red','119.99','If you like to game like your life depends on it, the Corsair K68 RGB backlit gaming keyboard is the piece of equipment for you. Keep your avatars alive and feel more like a part of the game with this mechanical gaming keyboard that features 100% gold-contact CHERRY MX mechanical switches and vibrant RGB customizable backlighting.','<ul><li>100% gold-contact CHERRY MX mechanical keyswitches provide a competitive advantage over your competition</li><li>Dynamic RGB backlighting, including brilliant red backlighting, enhances the experience and offers virtually unlimited lighting customization with CORSAIR Utility Engine</li><li>Instant illumination provided by on-board, pre-installed effects</li><li>Up to IP32 water and dust resistance to let you continue playing through the toughest of conditions</li><li>Adjust your audio as necessary with dedicated multimedia and volume controls</li><li>Full-key rollover ensures your commands and simultaneous keystrokes always register the way you intended for 100% anti-ghosting</li><li>Windows key lock mode prevents accidental Windows and Context Menu key presses</li><li>Detachable, soft-touch wrist rest provides comfort to enhance your gameplay</li></ul>'),('12649145','Logitech G613 LIGHTSPEED Wireless Mechanical','89.99','Logitech 920-008386 G613 LIGHTSPEED Wireless Mechanical Gaming Keyboard','<p>LIGHTSPEED wireless technology for super fast 1 ms report rate Romer-G mechanical switches deliver quiet, precise mechanical performance and 70 million click life for incredible feel and durability Six programmable G keys put custom macro sequences and in-app commands at your fingertips.1 Customize G key profiles individually for each app Multihost 2.4GHz + Bluetooth: Connect via LIGHTSPEED for super fast 1ms report rate or connect to multiple devices with multi-host Bluetooth connectivity. Batteries are not included.</p>'),('12727277','Mechanical Keyboard With LED Backlights ','72.99','Mechanical Gaming Keyboard With LED Backlights and Blue Switches for PC Gaming Compact ABS-Metal Design','<p>GAMING KEYBOARD; 104 Key Mechanical Gaming Keyboard with Custom Mechanical Switches(Cherry Blue equivalent) designed for longevity with greater durability and responsiveness. Fast mechanical keys with medium resistance, precise actuation, audible click sound, and tactile bump feedback.</p><p> MECHANICAL KEYBOARD; LED backlit mechanical gaming keyboard, the Red Led illuminated keyboard comes with Double-shot injection molded keycaps offering crystal clear uniform backlighting and lettering that doesn\'t scratch off.</p><p> ALUMINUM / ABS CONSTRUCTION; The PC Gaming keyboard is constructed of Aluminium and ABS with plate-mounted mechanical keys and switchesthat stand up to tough gaming conditions.</p><p> BACKLIT ANTI GHOSTING KEYBOARD; ALL 104 mechanical gaming keyboards keys are conflict free (n-Key Rollover) for ultimate Gaming performance.Featuring 12 Multimedia keys, Non-Slip Ergonomic, splash-proof Design. Comes with Full numeric keypad and a gold-plated corrosion free USB connector for a reliable connection.</p><p> PC GAMING KEYBOARD COMPATIBILTY: Windows 10, Windows 8, Windows 7, Windows Vista, or Windows XP, Limited Mac OS keyboard support</p>');
